The principal documents produced in a buyout are: 
 * Equity documents:
 * investment agreement; 
 * articles of association; 
 * employment agreements. 
 * Acquisition documents: 
 * share purchase or asset purchase agreement;
 * disclosure letter. 
 * Finance documents (if any): 
 * bank facility agreement;
 * bank security documents.

The Vermont Trade Secrets Act (VTSA) preempts conflicting remedies for trade 
secret misappropriation but does not affect certain remedies (9 V.S.A. § 4607; 
see Questions 3 and 13).

Sexual harassment is prohibited as a form of sex discrimination under the 
Wyoming Fair Employment Practices Act (WFEPA) (Wyo. Stat. Ann. § 27-9-105; 
Hoflund v. Airport Golf Club, 105 P.3d 1079, 1085 (Wyo. 2005)).
